params.message: This tests Tip Pick Up Failure (General Error for now)
Please remove tip rack from deck. When you're testing recovery, add tiprack back as necessary.
Use p50UL tips - Swap with tip(s) that are hot glued shut (you will need to swap the tips for retry recovery options)
This tests Liquid Presence Detection - PLEASE MAKE SURE YOU'RE USING 1000UL TIPS OR YOU WILL BREAK THE PIPETTE
Make sure reservoir is empty, and have full reservoir on standby to switch out with for recovery
Swap with tip(s) that are hot glued shut (you will need to cut the tips for retry recovery options)
You will have to manually remove tips if you're using a modified pipette

metadata.description: Simple Protocol that user can use to Phase 1 Error Recovery options for single and multi channel pipettes. NOTE: YOU WILL NEED A MODIFIED PIPETTE (NO SHROUD), and changed order of operations to reduce impact of dispense ER failure
